<h1>We received a request to reset the password on your Friends Next Door account.<h1>

<p>
  If you made this request, there's only one step left:
  Click the link below to confirm your identify and receive a new email.
</p>

<% if Rails.env.development? %>
  <a href="<%= "http://localhost:3000/password_reset/#{@str}" %>">Reset Password</a>
<% else %>
  <a href="<%= "http://csvw-project.herokuapp.com/password_reset/#{@str}" %>">Reset Password</a>
<% end %>

<p>
  If you did not make this request, you can safely ignore
  this email and no changes will be made to your account.
</p>
